B.De=s(["If I could give your heart one address, I would write my name beside peace and ask it to stay there forever.","You do not simply enter a room, you soften the air inside it.","I still think the luckiest thing I have ever done was meet you before I knew I needed you.","You make affection feel less like a word and more like a place I can live in.","Every version of tomorrow gets prettier when I imagine you in it.","You are my favorite kind of miracle, the quiet one that changes everything.","My heart stopped looking for poetry the day it realized it could just listen to you laugh.","You are the reason ordinary moments keep dressing up like memories.","Loving you feels like finding light in places I used to call ordinary.","I hope you know how gently the universe handled me when it sent me to you.","If home had a face, I think it would look a little like your smile.","You make being honest about love feel easy.","I could spend a lifetime learning your moods and still call it the shortest beautiful thing I ever did.","Your name has become my favorite answer to questions no one asks out loud.","I did not know peace could blush until I saw you smile at me.","When you look at me kindly, the whole day changes its mind about being difficult.","You are the softest certainty my heart has ever known.","I keep falling for the smallest things about you like they are the biggest blessings.","If I had to choose between sleep and talking to you, I would probably choose your voice and call that rest.","You are proof that tenderness can be unforgettable.","Some people write love letters, but you make my whole life want to become one.","You carry a kind of warmth that even my most guarded thoughts trust.","I hope every mirror in your world tells you the truth about how lovely you are.","My favorite thing about fate is that somehow it led me to you.","Even silence feels romantic when it is shared with you.","You are the pause in my chaos that never asks for anything except honesty.","I could lose track of time with you and still feel like I arrived exactly where I was supposed to be.","You make my heart behave like it has a song saved just for your arrival.","If sweetness were a season, you would be all four.","I adore you in ways that language is still trying to catch up with.","The world gets less heavy whenever I remember I get to care about you.","I would choose your hand in the dark over a thousand easier roads.","Your smile has the kind of power prayers wish they had.","I did not plan to care this deeply, but then you were yourself and that was the end of my resistance.","You make my heart feel seen without ever asking it to explain itself.","If I were ever brave enough to say everything I feel, your name would be in every sentence.","Your existence is my favorite interruption.","There is something about you that turns my thoughts into lanterns.","You have a beautiful habit of making life feel less rushed and more worth noticing.","I like who I become when I am loved by your presence.","You are the reason I believe softness can be stronger than certainty.","My heart trusts you the way flowers trust morning.","When I picture forever kindly, it always borrows something from you.","I do not need grand signs from the universe when your voice already feels like one.","You are the kind of person songs are trying to remember.","Some hearts race because of fear, mine does it because you exist.","I hope you never doubt the amount of wonder you leave behind when you simply show up.","I have met beautiful things before, but never something that made beauty feel understood until you.","If affection had a favorite person, I think it would choose you.","You make devotion feel less dramatic and more true.","I am fond of the way your presence turns me into a gentler version of myself.","Every little detail about you feels like the universe admitting it was showing off.","I could spend hours with you and still call it too short.","You are the part of my day I replay without trying.","I think my heart learned patience just to meet you properly.","There is no version of me that does not feel lucky around you.","You are the answer my quietest hopes were too shy to ask for.","If love had handwriting, it would probably look like your name in my notes.","You make me understand why people ruin perfectly good sleep just to keep talking.","You are lovely in the way rain is lovely when you are somewhere safe enough to enjoy it.","My favorite kind of peace is the one that arrives with your attention.","You are not just beautiful, you are beautifully felt.","I wish you could see yourself through the gratitude I carry for you.","Even my most guarded feelings sit a little closer to the door when you are near.","You make longing feel softer because somehow you also make hope feel real.","If I had a garden, I would name the gentlest flowers after the things I feel for you.","The sweetest thing about liking you is how natural it feels.","I do not think hearts are meant to be perfect, only sincere, and mine is very sincere about you.","You make forever sound less frightening and more like a promise worth keeping.","There is a kind of elegance in the way you make me care more carefully.","I did not know comfort could have chemistry until I met you.","You are my favorite reason to be a little more honest with my feelings.","My heart writes your name in margins I never meant to fill.","You make tenderness look effortless.","I think sunsets would envy the way you leave warmth behind.","You are the kind of person who makes even patience feel romantic.","My heart is not subtle about you, it brightens too quickly.","If the universe ever asks what I wanted most, I will say moments with you that lasted a little longer.","I like the way your existence gives my future a softer color.","You are my favorite proof that calm and excitement can live in the same person.","I could call you lovely all day and still feel like I missed the best parts.","With you, even anticipation feels like a gift.","You have a way of making affection feel intelligent, deliberate, and real.","My thoughts about you arrive dressed like daydreams.","You are the kind of feeling people protect with poems.","I hope life stays gentle with you, mostly because I know how much gentleness you bring into other lives.","Your laughter is the shortest road to my peace.","You are the type of beautiful that changes a room without making a sound.","Every time you are kind to me, something in my heart quietly chooses you again.","You make my world less noisy and more meaningful.","The nicest future I can imagine always has your smile somewhere inside it.","I think love becomes believable whenever you are being yourself.","You are the person my softer side would write to first.","Your presence feels like a secret blessing that forgot to stay secret.","I do not know how to explain it properly, but my heart relaxes when it reaches you.","If I could frame a feeling, I would frame the calm happiness of being noticed by you.","You are my favorite reason to romanticize real life.","You make me want to protect what is gentle in this world, starting with the way you are loved.","Your existence has a way of making even my careful heart act brave.","If this life gives me a thousand conversations, I want the best ones to be with you.","I could search every language and still return to the same truth: I like you more than words are built for.","You are the sweetest plot twist my heart never saw coming."],t.s)
